Package: ferroviz
Type: Package
Title: ferroviz package allows to highlight driver and suppressor ferroptosis genes
        in transcriptome differential expression gene analysis output from limma
        algorithm
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Christophe Desterke
Maintainer: The package maintainer <christophe.desterke@inserm.fr>
Description: ferroviz package allows to highlight driver and suppressor ferroptosis genes
        in transcriptome differential expression gene analysis output from limma
        algorithm.
        Ferroptosis related genes from ferrdbV2 were converted in orthologues with Biomart.
        This package could work for Mus musculus and Homo sapiens species.
License: GNU
Imports: dplyr, ggplot2, tidyr, ggrepel
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
